text:
From Kushagra:
'KG kaha milega? ' 
'Geetam ke room me hoga pakka' 
1st year summers me Pubg se shuru hui apni dosti. Noob se lekar pro ban gya, CC jaane waala ladka library jaane laga, 1st year tak gaali nhi deta tha aur aaj road par kisi random ko bhee gaali dene lagta hai... 'Kon canteen me paisa waste kare me to mess me daal fry le lunga'..... Se lekar...... 'Ab kitna bhee kharcha ho mujhe farak nhi padta'......Sab mera hee to influence haiğŸ˜ 
Raat ko CC se 1:55 par canteen pahuchne kaa target saath me poora karna, domino's waalo ko har week exploit karna, saath me har kisi ka mazak udaana, raat bhar campus me ghumna, manali me poore time aditya kee photo click karte rehna....aur pta nhi kya kya.
Thank you bro for everything, for all the masti we did together, for all the advices although teree baate mene kabhi na maani ache se...But ab try jaroor karunga.
Last me bas yahi kehna chaahunga - 
"Har har modi, ghar ghar modi"

text:
"Delhi developed hai kyuki agra me airport nahi hai !"  tera yeh statement hamesha yaad rahega yar. 

Second year se kaafi badhiya bonding hui tere saath, roommate hi ban gaya tha tu toh. Canteen chalne ke liye ever ready, Neend se utha ke leke jate the yaar tuze canteen. Mostly har wednesday ko phone-pay pe offers dekh ke pizza order karna and log generally chili flakes and oregano extra lete hai but tere liye tissues extra lene padte the. 

Raat me bulb ke upar polythene daal ke padhta tha yar tu. itni dedication kaha se laate ho bhaiyya, kaise kar lete ho yeh sab?  CCD se wapas ate waqt shailabh ke peeche bina chappal ke kya tez bhaga tha yar tu, maza hi aa gaya tha yar uss din toh.

Bohat memories hai yar, abhi toh ek saal aur hai hope ki aur badhiya badhiya memories banengi. Dua hai ki aise hi chaapta rahe and tere room me NAMI  ğŸ’¦  and SAFEDI ki chamkar bani rahe and hope ki future me only thing suicidal about you, will be your car doors.
author: Khemraj Sudhakar Bawaskar
